SUMMARY:Toddler Time at Hawaiian Falls Mansfield
LOCATION:Hawaiian Falls Mansfield\, Mansfield\, TX
DESCRIPTION:Source: Luma\n\n🌊 Toddler Time at Hawaiian Falls Mansfield 
 🌊\n\nJoin DFW Mom Society for an exclusive morning of splashing\, playi
 ng\, and connecting with other local moms and families before Hawaiian Fal
 ls opens to the public! Thank you to Arlington Pediatric Dentistry for spo
 nsoring this event.\n\nOn July 10 from 9:00 AM–10:30 AM\, children ages 
 7 and under will enjoy special early access to select attractions in a sma
 ller\, toddler-friendly environment. This is the perfect opportunity to le
 t your little ones play\, explore\, and make new friends while you connect
  with other families in the community.\n\nThe following attractions will b
 e open during Toddler Time:\n• Keiki Kove Kid's Area\n• Turtle Bay Act
 ivity Pool\n• Niko's Splash Pad\n• Wave Pool\n\nAdmission:\n• $9 per
  child ages 7 months-7 years\n• Additional siblings 6 months and younger
  are free\n• Children ages 3 and older with a Hawaiian Falls Season Pass
 : $6 admission\n• One complimentary adult is included with each paid chi
 ld ticket. Additional adults must purchase an adult ticket.\n• This even
 t is exclusively for children ages 7 and under. Any child who is 8 years o
 r older will not be admitted to this event.\n• Tickets will not be sold 
 at the door. You must purchase tickets from DFW Mom Society.\n\nImportant 
 Event Information:\n• You may begin lining up at 8:30 AM. Gates will ope
 n at 8:50 AM.\n• If you are only bringing a child who is 6 months old or
  younger\, you must still purchase one child ticket for admission. Only si
 blings 6 months and younger of paid children will be let in free.\n• No 
 children over the age of 7 will be admitted.\n• Small coolers are permit
 ted and may be brought in free of charge.\n• Our exclusive event time en
 ds at 10:30 AM. If you would like to remain in the park after 10:30 AM\, y
 ou will need to purchase additional admission according to Hawaiian Falls 
 policies.\n\nPlease note that Hawaiian Falls will open to Season Pass Hold
 ers at 10:00 AM and to the general public at 10:30 AM. Season Pass Holders
  will be asked to provide proof of their season pass at the entrance.\n\nP
 lease purchase a ticket for each child attending. There will be no refunds
  for this event\; however\, you are welcome to transfer or sell your ticke
 t to another family if you are unable to attend.\n\nWhether you're coming 
 with friends or hoping to meet new mom friends\, we'd love to have you joi
 n us for this special summer morning of fun!\n\nCalendar: Personal\n\nHost
 s: DFW Mom Society\n\nVenue: Hawaiian Falls Mansfield\n\nEvent page: https
 ://luma.com/uidcnb7h
URL:https://luma.com/uidcnb7h
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
