LOCATION:FULL CITY ROOSTER\, Dallas\, TX
DESCRIPTION:Source: Luma\n\nThis is our first little Dallas Creatives meetu
 p\, so most of us will probably be walking in without knowing anyone. This
  is the point.\n\nCome grab a coffee\, meet new people\, make a few creati
 ve friends\, and see who is out there. You do not have to call yourself a 
 “creative” to come. If you like good people\, fresh ideas\, or just wa
 nt to make new friends in Dallas\, you are welcome too.\n\nCalendar: Perso
 nal\n\nHosts: Brandie Janow\n\nVenue: FULL CITY ROOSTER\n\nEvent page: htt
 ps://luma.com/wurgkxie
