SUMMARY:Swap N Shop: A Free Mom Swap
LOCATION:Mansfield Fieldhouse\, Mansfield\, TX
DESCRIPTION:Source: Luma\n\nJoin us for a special morning of community\, ge
 nerosity\, and blessing other local families. Clean out what you no longer
  need and swap it for items your family will actually use! We will be insi
 de the gym at Fieldhouse USA. We will have some sensory tables out for the
  kids.\n\nThis is not an item-for-item swap — take whatever you need - f
 or free.\n\nWhat to bring (required to participate):\n• Minimum of 5 cle
 an\, gently-used baby or children's items\n• Clothing (up to kids size 6
 )\, toys\, books\, baby gear\, etc.\n• Bring as many items as you’d li
 ke!\n• No stained\, torn\, or broken items please\n\nHow it works:\n9:00
 -9:30 AM – Drop off your items in the designated areas + receive your sh
 opping ticket\n(Items will be self-sorted into designated areas - we recom
 mend sorting them according to size and gender before arriving to speed up
  the process)\n\n9:45 AM – Shopping begins for the first 25 moms\n• En
 try will be based on your ticket number which is given in order of arrival
 \n• Groups will be let in every few minutes\n• Take whatever your fami
 ly can use ♡\n\nWhat to expect:\n• A fun and free shopping experience\
 n• Toast and Roast will be there selling coffee\n• A chance to connect
  and enjoy some well-deserved girl time\n\nImportant notes:\n• Moms-only
  swap (no dads or resellers please)\n• Children are welcome\, we will ha
 ve sensory bins for the little ones. You are welcome to visit PlayPark MTX
  afterward.\n• Please bring your own bag — we will NOT have extras\n
 • All leftover items will be donated to Mansfield Mission Center\n\nCome
  shop\, connect\, and leave with items your family will love — we can’
 t wait to see you there ♡\n\nCalendar: Personal\n\nHosts: DFW Mom Societ
 y\n\nVenue: Mansfield Fieldhouse\n\nEvent page: https://luma.com/xvdzezh3
URL:https://luma.com/xvdzezh3
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
