SUMMARY:(Free) Dallas-area women's 35+ meetup\, Planter Painting
LOCATION:4003 San Mateo Dr\, Plano\, TX
DESCRIPTION:Source: Luma\n\nJoin us for a FREE relaxing and creative mornin
 g of Planter Painting with Amber\, designed especially for women 35+! 🎨
 ✨\n\nWe’ll provide everything you need to paint and decorate your own 
 clay pot\, including pots\, paints\, brushes\, and lots of creative inspir
 ation. Whether you love to paint or you’re picking up a brush for the fi
 rst time\, this experience is all about slowing down\, expressing yourself
 \, and enjoying the simple pleasure of creating something colorful and fun
 .\n\nNo experience necessary—just bring your curiosity and a willingness
  to try something new! Space is limited\, so be sure to register early to 
 save your seat. We can’t wait to spend this creative morning with you! 
 💫\n\nCalendar: Winona Meetups\n\nHosts: Winona Meetups\n\nVenue: 4003 S
 an Mateo Dr\n\nEvent page: https://luma.com/sjcng0ro
URL:https://luma.com/sjcng0ro
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
