SUMMARY:n8n Dallas Community Meetup
LOCATION:25N Coworking Frisco\, Frisco\, TX
DESCRIPTION:Source: Luma\n\nn8n Dallas Community Meetup\n\nDFW’s automati
 on community is getting together—and you’re invited.\n\nWhether you’
 re already building with n8n or just exploring what’s possible\, join us
  for a relaxed afternoon of networking\, knowledge sharing\, and hands-on 
 learning. Meet fellow builders\, exchange ideas\, and see real-world autom
 ation workflows and AI agents in action.\n\nWhat to Expect\n\n🤝 Network
 ing with the local automation community\n\n🎤 Quick introductions: What 
 are you automating in DFW?\n\n🛠️ Interactive workshop covering:\nWork
 flow automation\n\nAI agents\n\nIntegrations\n\nSelf-hosting\n\nBest pract
 ices and lessons learned\n\n🍽️ Lunch and informal discussions\n\nWho 
 Should Attend\n\nSoftware developers\, DevOps engineers\, and technical bu
 ilders\n\nRevOps\, Marketing Ops\, and Operations professionals\n\nFounder
 s and small teams looking to automate without hiring a large engineering t
 eam\n\nAnyone curious about n8n and looking for a welcoming first meetup\n
 \nSchedule\n\n12:00 PM — Doors open & networking\n\n12:15 PM — Welcome
  and community introductions\n\n12:35 PM — Workshop: Building automation
 s with n8n\, AI agents\, integrations\, and self-hosting\n\n2:30 PM — Lu
 nch & open networking\n\n2:50 PM — Community announcements and what’s 
 next for DFW\n\n3:00 PM — Event concludes\n\nEvent Details\n\nDate: Wedn
 esday\, July 22\, 2026\n\nTime: 12:00 PM – 3:00 PM CDT\n\nVenue: 25N Cow
 orking\, 9355 John W. Elliott Dr.\, Suite 25\, Frisco\, TX 75033\n\nAdmiss
 ion: Free\n\nRegistration: Required\n\nSpace is limited. If your plans cha
 nge\, please cancel your registration so someone on the waitlist can atten
 d.\n\nAbout the Host\n\nFakhar Khan is the volunteer n8n Community Ambassa
 dor for the Dallas–Fort Worth area. This meetup is a community-led educa
 tional event designed to connect builders\, share knowledge\, and grow the
  local automation ecosystem. It is not a sales event.\n\nQuestions? Feel f
 ree to contact the host through Luma.\n\n#n8n #Automation #AIAgents #DFW #
 Frisco\n\nCalendar: n8n Community Events\n\nHosts: n8n\, SOFT PYRAMID LLC\
 n\nVenue: 25N Coworking Frisco\n\nEvent page: https://luma.com/n8n-pg7a
URL:https://luma.com/n8n-pg7a
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:OPAQUE
