SUMMARY:Sensory Splash
LOCATION:Clayton W Chandler Park\, Mansfield\, TX
DESCRIPTION:Source: Luma\n\nCome join us for a morning of summer fun at the
  splash pad! We’ll have sensory bins\, bubbles\, snacks\, and more for k
 ids to explore and enjoy. 🌞\n\nWe’ll also offer a special sensory-fri
 endly time from 9:30–10:00 AM before the event officially begins. This q
 uieter time is designed for families who prefer a smaller crowd\, have chi
 ldren with sensory sensitivities\, or have little ones who benefit from a 
 calmer environment.\n\nA special thank you to Olive Physical Therapy in Ar
 lington for sponsoring this event! Their team will be on-site to connect w
 ith moms and share tips on pelvic floor health after childbirth.\n\nThank 
 you to the City of Mansfield for partnering with us on this event as part 
 of Project 365 this summer!\n\nIf this is your first time at one of our ev
 ents\, our Welcome Committee would love to help you feel at home and intro
 duce you to other moms. Just check the box when you register\, and we’ll
  be in touch. 💛\n\nCalendar: Personal\n\nHosts: DFW Mom Society\n\nVenu
 e: Clayton W Chandler Park\n\nEvent page: https://luma.com/n0kdyww1
