SUMMARY:Books\, Eggs & Coffee — July Book Club Meeting
LOCATION:Broken Yolk Cafe\, McKinney\, TX
DESCRIPTION:Source: Luma\n\nJuly book club meeting and we're making it a wh
 ole morning 🩷\n\nThis month we're reading Dear Debbie and we cannot wai
 t to sit down with you girls and talk all about it. Come ready with your t
 houghts\, your hot takes\, and your appetite because Broken Yolk Cafe put 
 together a special breakfast package just for us.\n\nFor $20 you get one e
 ntree plus a drink of your choice — coffee\, Pepsi products\, or apple j
 uice. Just show up\, order\, and pay at the restaurant. No prepayment need
 ed\, no stress\, just good food and great conversation with the best group
  of girls.\n\nSpots are limited so make sure you RSVP to secure your seat.
  Bring a girl with you because book club is always better with your people
  📖💚\n\nWe cannot wait to see you there 🩷\n\nDate: Saturday\, July
  25th\nTime: 9:30 — 11:00am\nLocation: Broken Yolk Cafe\, McKinney TX\nP
 rice: $20 per person — pay at the restaurant\nHost: The Pink Haus Club\n
 \nCalendar: Personal\n\nHosts: The Pink Haus Club\, The Pink Haus Club\n\n
 Venue: Broken Yolk Cafe\n\nEvent page: https://luma.com/qjfv48aa
