SUMMARY:IT and SecOps Happy Hour Dallas
LOCATION:Loro Asian Smokehouse & Bar\, Dallas\, TX
DESCRIPTION:Source: Luma\n\nAGENDA\n\n5:30–6:00 PM — Arrival & Welcome 
 Drinks\n6:00–7:30 PM — Networking + Food\n7:30–8:00 PM — Open Netw
 orking & Closing\n\nABOUT\n\nJoin a select group of IT and SecOps leaders 
 in Dallas for an evening of industry conversation\, great food\, and netwo
 rking\, swapping stories and making real connections with fellow leaders a
 nd operators.\n\nIf you work in IT\, IAM\, GRC\, or SecOps and are interes
 ted in how AI is transforming internal support\, we’d love to have you.\
 n\nSpots are limited and registration is subject to approval.\n\nHOST\n\nC
 onsole is an AI agent that automates employee support (IT\, Security\, HR\
 , and more)\, designed to adapt to how your organization works. It learns 
 from your existing knowledge base\, runbooks\, and app matrix to handle re
 quests like app access\, account lockouts\, and troubleshooting\, just lik
 e a tier-1 analyst would.\n\nLive with companies like Databricks\, Faire\,
  Cursor\, Figma\, etc. Console automates 75%+ of tickets while acting as a
  proactive teammate\, constantly identifying gaps and suggesting improveme
 nts to your processes.\n\nLearn more here\n\nFollow Console on Linkedin\n\
 nWe're hiring! Join our team\n\nCalendar: Console\n\nHosts: Jackie Lu\, Ja
 cob Neel\n\nVenue: Loro Asian Smokehouse & Bar\n\nEvent page: https://luma
 .com/ConsoleDallas
URL:https://luma.com/ConsoleDallas
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
