SUMMARY:The Mermaid Experience
LOCATION:Howard Moore Play Pool\, Arlington\, TX
DESCRIPTION:Source: Luma\n\n🧜‍♀️ Mermaid Experience 🧜‍♀️\
 n\nJoin us for a magical morning with a real mermaid at Howard Moore Play 
 Pool in Arlington! ✨\n\nWe’ve rented out the entire play pool exclusiv
 ely for our group from 9:30–11:30 AM\, and a mermaid (tail and all) will
  be waiting in the shallow end to interact with your little ones\, take ph
 otos\, and create a memorable experience they won’t forget.\n\n🎟️ L
 imited to only 100 tickets!\nEvery guest 12 months and older must have a t
 icket - including moms. If you don’t have a ticket\, you won’t be let 
 in.\n\nThis event is designed for our littlest swimmers\, so we ask that m
 oms only bring children ages 7 and under to help keep the experience safe 
 and enjoyable for everyone.\n\n💦 About Howard Moore Play Pool:\nThis in
 teractive shallow-water play pool is perfect for young children and featur
 es:\n• Interactive water play structure\n• Shallow water designed for 
 ages 7 and under\n• Pool chairs surrounding the play area\n• Shade umb
 rellas\n• Family changing room\n• Small grassy areas\n\nWe’ll have s
 nacks and drinks available for moms to enjoy. You’re also welcome to bri
 ng your own snacks\, water bottles\, and favorite pool toys!\n\nCome make 
 some sweet summer memories with us! 🧜‍♀️💙\n\nCalendar: Persona
 l\n\nHosts: DFW Mom Society\n\nVenue: Howard Moore Play Pool\n\nEvent page
 : https://luma.com/op9i0ohi
URL:https://luma.com/op9i0ohi
